playbackDescription.title: Neural Networks
playbackDescription.description:
This program creates a relatively simple neural network in C++. The neural network can learn from training data and can predict outputs based on any input. At the end of the program I use the neural network to learn a game strategy for a simple role playing game.

I take an object-oriented approach to developing the neural network code. The primary classes relate to managing Neurons and Layers. There are more sophisticated machine learning libraries out there that are more appropriate for real world problems but I believe there is value in walking through this code to understand how neural networks work.
